games.comment: Ray Rice split carries. McClain had 86 yards, while Rice managed 64 on 22 rushes.

Ray Rice were able to do much on the ground much after that. Pierce tallied 28 yards on 5 carries, while Rice mustered only 15 yards on 6 tries, though he did catch 7 balls for 35 receiving yards. Rice was sidelined for much of the first half with an injury.    The Bengals had slightly more success on the ground.
